channel.title: Compiler Error (Server Side)
channel.description:
Well while I was coding and got everything done... I ran across an error and at first it was like this
session.getFilterChain().addLast("protocolFilter"; new ProtocolCodecFilter(new GameCodecFactory(inC)));
And it said it was missing ')' at the end of "protocolFilter" so I added it and then it gave me another error (Before the adding of ")" I had 100 errors cause the whole code for protocolFilter was messed up. [img]http://i214.photobucket.com/albums/cc6/man1412/Commpilerissue.jpg[/img] Any help with this would be very greatful. Thanks very much
